description:
Actress, environmental activist, and wellness icon Jane Fonda has learned a lot in her 83 years. In this interview, she talks to us about the privilege of good health, how her relationships have affected her self-esteem and appearance, her love of hemp-oil face masks (she’s an Uncle Bud’s spokesperson), and the power of a good lip liner. -- Want more of our beauty podcast?
